<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٥ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٨ص١٣٥:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: {لَعَمْرُكَ إِنَّهُمْ لَفِي سَكْرَتِهِمْ يَعْمَهُونَ <span class="c2">(٧٢)</span> فَأَخَذَتْهُمُ الصَّيْحَةُ مُشْرِقِينَ <span class="c2">(٧٣)</span> فَجَعَلْنَا عَالِيَهَا سَافِلَهَا وَأَمْطَرْنَا عَلَيْهِمْ حِجَارَةً مِنْ سِجِّيلٍ <span class="c2">(٧٤)</span> إِنَّ فِي ذَلِكَ لَآيَاتٍ لِلْمُتَوَسِّمِينَ <span class="c2">(٧٥)</span> وَإِنَّهَا لَبِسَبِيلٍ مُقِيمٍ <span class="c2">(٧٦)</span> إِنَّ فِي ذَلِكَ لَآيَةً لِلْمُؤْمِنِينَ <span class="c2">(٧٧)</span> وَإِنْ كَانَ أَصْحَابُ الْأَيْكَةِ لَظَالِمِينَ <span class="c2">(٧٨)</span> فَانْتَقَمْنَا مِنْهُمْ وَإِنَّهُمَا لَبِإِمَامٍ مُبِينٍ <span class="c2">(٧٩)</span> وَلَقَدْ كَذَّبَ أَصْحَابُ الْحِجْرِ الْمُرْسَلِينَ <span class="c2">(٨٠)</span>} <span class="c4">[الحجر: ٧٢ - ٨٠]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ ابْنُ عَبَّاسٍ:</span> <span class="c3">{لَعَمْرُكَ}</span>: <span class="c2">«لَعَيْشُكَ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>-<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص٨٠:</span> <span class="c3">{الصَّيْحَةُ}</span>: <span class="c2">«الهَلَكَةُ»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>-<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٤ص١٤٨:</span> <span class="c3">{لِلْمُتَوَسِّمِينَ}</span>: <span class="c2">«لِلنَّاظِرِينَ»</span>،<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c3">{وَإِنَّهَا لَبِسَبِيلٍ}</span>: <span class="c2">«لَبِطَرِيقٍ»</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>-<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١١١:</span> وَقَالَ مُجَاهِدٌ: <span class="c2">(لَيْكَةُ)</span>: الأَيْكَةُ، وَهِيَ جَمْعُ الشَّجَرٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>-<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص٨٠:</span> <span class="c3">{لَبِإِمَامٍ مُبِينٍ}</span>: <span class="c2">«عَلَى الطَّرِيقِ»</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c3">{لَبِإِمَامٍ مُبِينٍ}</span>: <span class="c2">«الإِمَامُ كُلُّ مَا ائْتَمَمْتَ وَاهْتَدَيْتَ بِهِ»</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>-<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٤ص١٤٨:</span> <span class="c3">{الحِجْرِ}</span>: <span class="c2">«مَوْضِعُ ثَمُودَ»</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>